# Author Images Directory

This directory contains profile images for authors featured on the website.

## Organization:
- Use author ID as the filename (e.g., `william-shakespeare.jpg`)
- Supported formats: JPG, PNG, WebP
- Recommended sizes:
  - Thumbnail: 150x150px
  - Medium: 300x300px  
  - Large: 600x600px

## Naming Convention:
- `{author-id}.jpg` - Main profile image
- `{author-id}-thumb.jpg` - Thumbnail version
- `{author-id}-medium.jpg` - Medium size version
- `{author-id}-large.jpg` - Large size version
